                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/3861: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_RPS1"
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Reinsch</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1919-02-15T17:15:00-05:00"
                            notBefore="1919-02-14T19:00:00+04:53">
                            <hi rend="italic">undated</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received February 15, 1919, 5:15 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Following from [<persName corresp="#p_HEL1">Harris</persName> at] Tomsk.</p>
                <p>“112. February 14, 7 p.m. General Staff Omsk states today’s date that military
                    situation much improved during past three days’ fighting. Siberians have taken
                    many prisoners and guns. Fifteen Bolshevik regiments have refused to fight.
                    However as an offset to this four regiments of <persName>Dutoff</persName>’s
                    Cossacks have also refused to fight. Population Omsk quiet.</p>
                <p>Considerable enthusiasm over improved military situation. <persName
                        corresp="#p_HEL1">Harris</persName>.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_RPS1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Reinsch</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
